{
  "stem": "214.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so I wanted to-- and then, in the meanwhile, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I mean, when Rabbi Eskin, when we came to-- to Stuttgart, and opened this DP camp, which actually was a small beautiful villa in [INAUDIBLE], because there were very few of us at the time.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and a-- a short time later, the Joint Distribution Committee opened an office.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And one day I received a letter from the Joint, that-- somebody communicated with me on the Joint-- that actually it was, you know, some people, I suppose some people are businesspeople.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And some, even among our girls, and some went into business.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, they were buying cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were selling cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were doing this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They were doing that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, I was always-- but I was trying to find a job to do something until, whatever, you know, things will be disposed of.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I spoke to one of the-- he was a nice fellow, I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was an officer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And that-- I mean, it was-- some officer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Kurtz was his name, who, because they opened an American-- what do you call, military service, military offices, we used to call them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I applied for a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got the job, granted, maybe for two or three months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was supposed to be-- and in the meanwhile, I started taking English lessons.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I spoke-- I really spoke perfect German at that time-- that I should be a special investigator-- it sounded great-- for public health issues.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Which meant that I should-- this was a field job-- to go to-- well, you had-- you had pharmacies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't have drug stores, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
